{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1195410/extras/totg.png?t=1585912114\" /><br><br>Trial of the Gods is a collectible card game based in the world of Siralim. Collect creature cards with unique traits and use them to battle against the gods.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 100+ cards to collect that are based on creatures from the Siralim series! Each card has a unique trait that changes the way it works in battle.<br></li><li> Full-length campaign featuring over 90 battles, along with a hard mode.<br></li><li> Post-game content that features randomly generated battles. Win these matches to empower your cards and make them stronger!<br></li><li> Matches take only a few minutes to complete, lending the game a &quot;just one more round&quot; style of play.<br></li><li> Gameplay is based on Triple Triad and Tetra Master from Final Fantasy.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1195410/extras/01.png?t=1585912114\" /><br><br>Travel the 15 realms of Rodia and challenge the gods! Each realm consists of 6 battles. You will be rewarded with new cards and experience points for winning these battles, allowing you to experiment with new deck compositions to ensure your victory.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1195410/extras/02.png?t=1585912114\" /><br><br>Each card has unique stats and a trait that changes the way they work in battle. Use the Skeleton to snipe your foes from afar, or utilize a kamikaze-style attack with the Apis. The possibilities are endless!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1195410/extras/03.png?t=1585912114\" /><br><br>Siralim games are known for their insane amount of post-game content, and Trial of the Gods is no different! After you finish the campaign, you'll unlock a Hard Mode that is sure to challenge even the best of players. In addition, you will gain access to the Itherian Realms - randomly generated battles that allow you to empower your cards if you win, giving them increased stats.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Upper Hand I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1195410/a4537354372f02a08050db9052cd2f7fb07f4eeb.jpg"},{"name":"Upper Hand II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1195410/00228f56446b49413fc3f8cf66bc52a2cf4e249e.jpg"},{"name":"Upper Hand III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1195410/6714971d4f6da69c98d4a6bee7711c6331846a33.jpg"},{"name":"Powerhouse I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1195410/2e73d6a15f5fa100424707f13c6b115e91275e85.jpg"},{"name":"Powerhouse II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1195410/27780faec62d8148ea6175d256bc6f1728ec0b50.jpg"},{"name":"Powerhouse III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1195410/9d70f7b37c81530a7ddf4d84b6202261ee3f0979.jpg"},{"name":"Champion I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1195410/ade1b92cba986143f865f707853661d95cc01cbe.jpg"},{"name":"Champion II","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1195410/1165dbe4dd1d823918ae772dc4d50bcf2e1c52d8.jpg"},{"name":"Champion III","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1195410/c1ddb809a2731b2b5b48ce74980daac1d13715bc.jpg"},{"name":"Scholar I","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1195410/35a147c53d9381c11f7fe2f86d19df76d1b807fb.jpg"}],"total":40},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1195410/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1585912114","background_raw":"https://